precis:
Order authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs (a) to sign a CONVENTION
between Canada and LUXEMBOURG for the AVOIDANCE OF DOUBLE TAXATION and the
PREVENTION of FISCAL EVASION with respect to TAXES ON INCOME and on
CAPITAL, or (b) to issue an Instrument of Full Powers authorizing other
representatives to sign the Convention on behalf of Canada.
